T = int(input())
while T > 0:
    (n, x) = [int(i) for i in input().split(' ')]
    if x < n:
        print('-1')
        T -= 1
        continue
    a1 = x - n + 1
    ans = [str(a1)]
    ans = ans + [str(i) for i in range(1, n + 1) if i != a1]
    print(' '.join(ans))
    T -= 1
